{"tid":2033022,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"燉冰強一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑","createTime":"2020-05-24T11:40:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-25T06:56:37.000Z","uid":74203,"like":94,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c84f602dac39173cbafb60f4f84b563e12e44b8d","tid":2033022,"uid":74203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:40:54.000Z","msg":"燉冰強一到店，所有喝酒的人便都看著他笑，有的叫道：「燉冰強，你手下又做豬隊友了！」他不回答，對櫃裹說：「溫兩碗酒，要一碟茴香豆。」但沒有拿出銀兩。他們又故意的高聲嚷道：「你手下一定又偷了人家的東西了！」燉冰強睜大眼晴說：「你怎麼這樣憑空污人清白......」「什麼清白？我fb上親眼見你手下偷了ok的水，影到晒。」燉冰強便漲紅了臉，額上的青筋條條綻出，爭辯道：「後數不能算偷......後數！......執法者的事，能算偷麼？」接連便是難懂的話，什麼「忠誠勇毅」，什麼「執法」之類，引得眾人都哄笑起來：政總內外充滿了快活的空氣。"},{"pid":"8324f64b2e5aaa366e8df19a8c6b03053bf353a0","tid":2033022,"uid":74203,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:41:09.000Z","msg":"呢篇文真係萬能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4c238779d917ba79b298bef29330bc0bb69e268","tid":2033022,"uid":157901,"like":2,"dislike":26,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"拉 有時間寫呢啲on9文打飛機自己講自己笑不如推twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"639d6a1fe4115017e1500e7b885bc5b82da0e143","tid":2033022,"uid":74203,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"a4c238779d917ba79b298bef29330bc0bb69e268","tid":2033022,"uid":157901,"like":2,"dislike":26,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"拉 有時間寫呢啲on9文打飛機自己講自己笑不如推twitter<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:43:09.000Z","msg":"你又知我無"},{"pid":"da267c99d26d0e2d59fab493848d43cbd57369d6","tid":2033022,"uid":3976,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"quote":{"pid":"639d6a1fe4115017e1500e7b885bc5b82da0e143","tid":2033022,"uid":74203,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"a4c238779d917ba79b298bef29330bc0bb69e268","tid":2033022,"uid":157901,"like":2,"dislike":26,"score":-24,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-24T11:42:34.000Z","msg":"